## **Study Tips for Success**

1. **Consistency:** Study daily, even if just 30 minutes
2. **Hands-on:** Do ALL labs and activities (critical!)
3. **Flashcards:** Review daily, especially port numbers
4. **Subnetting:** Practice subnetting every single day
5. **Videos:** Watch Professor Messer's entire course (free on YouTube)
6. **Practice exams:** Take at least 3 full practice exams
7. **Document:** Create your own study notes
8. **Teach:** Explain concepts to others (best way to learn)
9. **Focus on weak areas:** Spend extra time on topics you struggle with
10. **Rest:** Don't cram the night beforeâ€”rest and confidence matter!

